OL,4,Ctwo-child benefit cap
OL,6,FThe cap affects some 1.6 million
OL,7,Fchildren, and as child poverty rates
OL,8,Frise, the PM has faced calls from
OL,9,Fcharities, opposition parties and some
OL,10,Fof his own backbench MPs to scrap the
OL,11,Flimit.
OL,13,FThe Commons Speaker has selected an
OL,14,FSNP amendment to the King's Speech
OL,15,Fcalling for the cap to be axed, and
OL,16,Fleft-wing Labour MPs are expected to
OL,17,Fweigh in further to a debate.
