OL,6,FMPs will vote on the proposed change
OL,7,Fon Tuesday evening. While the
OL,8,Fgovernment are not expected to lose
OL,9,Fthe vote due to their large majority,
OL,10,Fit will be the first test to see how
OL,11,Fmany backbench Labour MP's rebel.
OL,13,FThe SNP amendment is understood to
OL,14,Fhave the support of former Labour
OL,15,Fleader and now Independent MP Jeremy
OL,16,FCorbyn, some other left-wing Labour
OL,17,Fbackbenchers, and Green and Plaid
OL,18,FCymru MPs.
