OL,6,FOne of her children was in hospital
OL,7,Fwith a brain tumour at the time, and
OL,8,Fthe family also lost their house
OL,9,Fbecause of rising living costs.
OL,11,F"Whilst I was trying to support my
OL,12,Fson, I also had the stress of finding
OL,13,Fsomewhere else to live", Rebecca told
OL,14,FITV News.
OL,16,FShe said the cap has a huge impact on
OL,17,Ftheir family: "The kids have to go
OL,18,Fwithout a lot of the basic things. I
OL,19,Fthink the kids are suffering more than
OL,20,Fthe adults to be honest, even though
OL,21,Fthe bills are addressed to us."
