OL,6,FJoe Lane, Head of Policy and Research
OL,7,Fand Action for Children told ITV News
OL,8,Flifting the cap could also "lift
OL,9,Fhundreds of thousands of children out
OL,10,Fof poverty overnight."
OL,12,FHe urged the government to take action
OL,13,Fand scrap the cap: "The costs of
OL,14,Fhaving children grow up in poverty
OL,15,Foutweigh the costs of lifting them out
OL,16,Fof poverty", he said.
OL,18,FSNP Westminster leader Stephen Flynn
OL,19,Furged Scottish Labour MPs to back the
OL,20,Fparty's amendment to remove the cap.
